                        <p>Changes in 2.0 Beta 3:</p>
                        <ul>
                                <li>Vastly improved DSML file output.  10 times less memory and twice as fast!</li>
                                <li>New postEventWait event subsetter.  Check out <a href="realtime.html">these realtime considerations</a> to see how it works.</li>
                                <li>SOD will no longer retry event channel pairs until the end of time</li>
                                <li>SOD will warn you if you're running a new version of SOD on an old database, and if you've changed config files between runs on a single database</li>
